Package com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.parser.yamlParser.scriptItems.storeDefault

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractStoreDefaultParser
    Abstract class that defines the method for parsing default items.
    StoreDefaultCookieParser  
    StoreDefaultHeaderParser
    Parses the Headers list item to a List<StoreDefault> which consists of multiple StoreDefaultHeader.
    StoreDefaultItemParser
    Parses a simple key-value-item that is neither Constants.HEADERS, nor Constants.PARAMETERS, nor Constants.STATIC.
    StoreDefaultParameterParser
    Parses the Parameters list item to a List<StoreDefault> which consists of multiple StoreDefaultParameter.
    StoreDefaultStaticParser
    Parses the Static list item to a List<StoreDefault> which consists of multiple StoreDefaultStatic.
